---
---

<section class="ps" aria-labelledby="ps-problem-heading">
  <div class="ps-container">

    <!-- Problem -->
    <div class="ps-block ps-block--problem" data-animate="fade-up">
      <div class="ps-eyebrow">The Problem</div>
      <h2 id="ps-problem-heading" class="ps-heading">
        Barriers to opportunity are holding back<br />
        <em>career growth and stability</em>
      </h2>
      <p class="ps-body">
        Too many Latinos, women, young adults, and single mothers are held back
        not by lack of potential, but by limited access to affordable education,
        professional networks, job training, and real employment
        opportunities—barriers that prevent career growth and long-term stability.
      </p>
      <p class="ps-body ps-body--accent">
        Adriana's Foundation exists to change that.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Divider -->
    <div class="ps-divider" aria-hidden="true">
      <span class="ps-divider-line"></span>
      <span class="ps-divider-dot"></span>
      <span class="ps-divider-line"></span>
    </div>

    <!-- Solution -->
    <div class="ps-block ps-block--solution" data-animate="fade-up">
      <div class="ps-eyebrow ps-eyebrow--solution">Our Solution</div>
      <h2 class="ps-heading">
        We don't just educate.<br />
        <em>We prepare students for real careers.</em>
      </h2>
      <p class="ps-body">
        Our program combines foundational education, technical training,
        mentorship, internships, and job placement support to help students
        build long-term economic stability.
      </p>
      <a href="/academy" class="ps-cta">
        Learn How It Works
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ps {
    background: var(--color-bg-light-gray);
    padding: 6rem 0;
  }

  .ps-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .ps-block {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ps-eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-terracotta);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    padding: 0.35rem 0.875rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(6, 87, 154, 0.25);
    border-radius: 2rem;
  }

  .ps-eyebrow--solution {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    border-color: rgba(233, 173, 0, 0.4);
  }

  .ps-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.2vw, 3.25rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-bg-dark);
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .ps-heading em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-gold);
  }

  .ps-block--solution .ps-heading em {
    color: var(--color-terracotta);
  }

  .ps-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .ps-body--accent {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-terracotta);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .ps-divider {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }

  .ps-divider-line {
    display: block;
    width: 4rem;
    height: 1px;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .ps-divider-dot {
    width: 0.5rem;
    height: 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-gold);
  }

  .ps-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    background: var(--color-gold);
    color: var(--color-bg-dark);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 3rem;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(233, 173, 0, 0.25);
  }

  .ps-cta:hover {
    background: #FFD040;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(233, 173, 0, 0.35);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .ps {
      padding: 4rem 0;
    }

    .ps-divider {
      margin: 3rem 0;
    }

    .ps-divider-line {
      width: 2.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
